               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat prayer against evil eye and charm, The Legend of Susǝnyos and the witch Wurzǝlya, (accordion-fold book)</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="7r" facs="003">Fols 1r–7r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against evil eve and charm</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓይነ፡ ጥላ፡ ገርጋሪያ፡ ዓይነ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ዓይነ፡ ቡዳ፡ ወዓይነ፡ ጠቢብ፡ ዓይነ፡ መቅኛ፡ ወዓይነ፡ ወትንኰልኛ፡ መንኛ፡ ወጕሥምት፡ ወለሕማመ፡ አስወንውንውን፡ ወለሽንትምፅ፡ ወጐርኍሆ፡ ወጊርባ፡ ጀርባ፡...
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="7v" to="14r" facs="010">Fols 7v–14r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1763Legend">Ṣalot za-qǝddus
                                                  Susǝnyos baʾǝnta ʾasassǝlo dawe</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ዓይን፡ ሾትላይ፡ ወሀሎ፡ ፩ዱ፡ አምላክ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ሱስንዮስ፡
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
